         <abstract>
            <p>Nonlinear versions of the Lie-Trotter product formula $\exp\lbrack t(A + B) \rbrack = \lim_{n \rightarrow \infty} \lbrack\exp((t/n)A)\exp((t/n)B) \rbrack^n$ and related formulas are given in this paper. The convergence rates are optimal. The results are applicable to some nonlinear partial differential equations.</p>
          </abstract>
